observationText: The NCC-MPNST3-X2-C1 cell line had a doubling time of 58 hours.
The NCC-MPNST3-X2-C1 cell line exhibited weak invasive potential in in vitro invasion assays.
The NCC-MPNST3-X2-C1 cell line harbored the potential to form spheroids.
The NCC-MPNST3-X2-C1 cell line was found to be negative for Mycoplasma contamination based on PCR testing.
